text: Irsayevo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Irsayevsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 531 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 3 km from Mishkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Irsayevo
